data.text:
Join Six Feet Up and JetBrains for the 2nd annual, 3 day, multi-track Python Web Conference.

Tutorials: June 17, 2020 from 8:30 am ET to 5:00 pm ET (UTC -4h)

Talks: June 18-19, 2020 from 8:30 am ET to 5:00 pm ET (UTC -4h)

Location: This will be a virtual conference! You can join and participate from the comfort of your home office.

Register BELOW & receive:

Choose from 6 expert-led tutorials

Access up to 40+ presentations

Get an exclusive pass to recordings

Access the digital swag bag with goodies from our sponsors

Cast your vote for next year's topics
